article.headline: Alabama A&M 67, Prairie View 50
article.story: PRAIRIE VIEW, Texas (AP) -- Obie Trotter scored 13 points and had eight assists Monday to lead Alabama A&M to a 67-50 victory over Prairie View. Rick Ricketts added 12 points, all on 3-pointers, and Marcus Young added 11 for Alabama A&M (10-9, 7-2 Southwestern Athletic). Oscar Thompson led Prairie View (3-15, 3-6) with 16 points and Phillip Scott added 15. Alabama A&M led 34-29 at the half. Alabama A&M shot 46 percent from the field to only 32 percent for Prairie View.
